@startuml
!include _yunlink_protocol_theme.iuml
title Sunray Bridge Roadmap

rectangle "v1 Raw Control Bridge" <<Control>> as V1 {
  component "ROS1 only" as V1A
  component "single UAV /\nsingle session" as V1B
  component "Takeoff / Land /\nReturn / Goto /\nVelocitySetpoint" as V1C
  component "bridge-owned\nCommandResult" as V1D
}

rectangle "v2 Planning Bridge" <<StatePlane>> as V2 {
  component "planning_cmd /\nplanning_state" as V2A
  component "TrajectoryChunk\ntrue bridge" as V2B
  component "VehicleEvent\nformalized" as V2C
}

rectangle "Future Portability" <<Neutral>> as V3 {
  component "ROS2 adapter layer" as V3A
  component "shared mapping /\ntracker core" as V3B
  component "same Yunlink protocol\nowner model" as V3C
}

V1 --> V2 : expand semantic surface
V2 --> V3 : keep module split\nros_adapter isolated

note bottom
一期先把 owner、边界、回包语义和 raw control 闭环做对。
二期再扩 planning，而不是一开始混在一起。
end note
@enduml
